metadata.name: The Window
metadata.description:
This digital artwork was created using a blend of Ai and my photography, I have tried to give an empty scene life with an ai generated model, as if captured in a candid way.

When I originally took this photograph of a restaurant window in London, I had in mind that it would be a more interesting image if it had a human element and some life. Unfortunately I was on my own when I took the shot, and the street was empty and lifeless. I created the model in Mid Journey and gave her an intricate, detailed pattern on her dress, to compliment the colours pouring through the window of the restaurant onto the street.

Ai technology has enabled me to bring new depths to some of my photography, to create characters to fit the scene and tell a new story. 

AI Generator: Mid journey 
Location: London, England
 Edition: 1/1 Year: 2023 
Artist/Photographer: Rob Dawkins 
Dimensions: 2000 x 3000
